{
  "stem": "24409.11",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And our people wanted to find out what happened to their families, wanted to go to their hometown and find out their-- and they couldn't go because they were not supposed to speak to Germans.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] our commanding officer, Major [INAUDIBLE], was a member of the Philadelphia [INAUDIBLE] old family group that has given into our-- in fact, our whole unit thought that we should have some representation.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you got all European Jews so that somebody [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was important you spoke the right way of English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was called by his head [INAUDIBLE] said, what's happened to your-- to your unit?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said they don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Production went down so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he called me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And maybe he asked others too about what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you know this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I'm very aware of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, he said, oh, real-- real loner, works alone [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I told him about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, what shall-- shall we do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What shall we do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that will give us permission to look in our home towns for our relatives.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he gave permission for-- for two jeeps to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One left for Theresienstadt, which was occupied by the-- by American troops in Bohemia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Terezin, which was a kind of concentration camp, but it was a very mild concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was more a detention camp and a collection point to send to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other one was just-- I want to go to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had no idea that there was a strict-- a very strict rule to keep away from the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the borders had not been established yet, and Americans were afraid of-- of diplomatic complications.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the GIs who might be [INAUDIBLE], might be a [INAUDIBLE], and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
